{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"1eb201c9-46da-4cbd-89bd-b4fd15c73c80","content":"In your `App.xaml.cs`, override `CreateWindow` and subscribe to the lifecycle events:\n\n```csharp\nprotected override Window CreateWindow(IActivationState? activationState)\n{\n    var window = base.CreateWindow(activationState);\n\n    window.Created += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Created\");\n    window.Activated += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Activated\");\n    window.Deactivated += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Deactivated\");\n    window.Stopped += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Stopped\");\n    window.Resumed += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Resumed\");\n    window.Destroying += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Destroying\");\n    window.Backgrounding += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Backgrounding\");\n\n    return window;\n}\n```\n\n**Event flow:**\n\n| Transition | Events fired |\n|---|---|\n| App launch | Created → Activated |\n| Sent to background | Deactivated → Stopped (→ Backgrounding on iOS/Mac) |\n| Returned to foreground | Resumed → Activated |\n| App closed | Destroying |\n\n> `Backgrounding` only fires on iOS/Mac Catalyst and provides a `BackgroundingEventArgs` with a `State` dictionary you can use to persist data.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"bef87906-74a2-4e6a-a737-6b1e84d35127","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about subscribing to Window lifecycle events in a .NET MAUI app for debugging purposes. This is a general knowledge question about .NET MAUI that I can answer directly without needing to search the codebase.\n\nIn .NET MAUI, the `Window` class exposes several lifecycle events that correspond to the app's state transitions. Let me provide a concise, helpful answer.\n\nThe Window lifecycle events in .NET MAUI are:\n- Created\n- Activated\n- Deactivated\n- Stopped\n- Resumed\n- Destroying\n- Backgrounding (iOS/Mac Catalyst)\n\nI'll provide a code snippet showing how to subscribe to all of them.","outputTokens":504,"requestId":"0823:1ED665:A637E1:BFF267:69F2A846"},"id":"7841925d-5c21-4bd5-9755-1810f0cf4a25","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:54:40.678Z","parentId":"711aa769-3a31-492d-8555-e60c8dbbb7ec"}
